1
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#474239">Episode 10</font></font></font>

2
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#222522">"Eleven's Request"</font></font></font>

3
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your payment for the job.</font>

4
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also...</font>

5
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I looked into that matter for you.</font>

6
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive as always, 
Stud. You work quickly.</font>

7
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I tell you here?</font>

8
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it won't cause trouble for you.</font>

9
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

10
00:01:57,240 --> 00:02:00,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You had a long talk with 
him again this morning.</font>

11
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd asked him for a small favor.</font>

12
00:02:04,030 --> 00:02:05,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

13
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's your third of the reward.</font>

14
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:13,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! I wasn't planning on getting paid.</font>

15
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You worked the hardest. It's only proper.</font>

16
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay with that, Blade?</font>

17
00:02:20,110 --> 00:02:22,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's our leader's decision.</font>

18
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then don't mind if I do.</font>

19
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome.</font>

20
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

21
00:02:35,090 --> 00:02:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The usual?</font>

22
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, please.</font>

23
00:02:43,070 --> 00:02:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I discuss something private?</font>

24
00:02:48,850 --> 00:02:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you need the room?</font>

25
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'd like to speak with you.</font>

26
00:02:55,860 --> 00:03:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Merchant's guild staff and adventurers 
have met in that room, yes?</font>

27
00:03:06,450 --> 00:03:07,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

28
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are a few groups.</font>

29
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They meet roughly once a 
month, carrying luggage.</font>

30
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't be sure, but a group matching 
that description has been here.</font>

31
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did they last come?</font>

32
00:03:24,070 --> 00:03:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About a month ago.</font>

33
00:03:25,970 --> 00:03:28,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then they'll come again soon.</font>

34
00:03:28,230 --> 00:03:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What time do they arrive?</font>

35
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Always around this time.</font>

36
00:03:34,930 --> 00:03:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome.</font>

37
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two glasses of that whisky.</font>

38
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought they'd come today or 
tomorrow. What good timing.</font>

39
00:03:54,390 --> 00:03:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do anything crazy.</font>

40
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't.</font>

41
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm meeting someone.</font>

42
00:04:02,210 --> 00:04:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's already here.</font>

43
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:06,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice night, isn't it?</font>

44
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long do they normally stay?</font>

45
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thirty minutes at most. 
They don't stay long.</font>

46
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps I should've 
brought someone with me.</font>

47
00:04:26,590 --> 00:04:30,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to pass the time 
at a bar when I can't drink.</font>

48
00:04:35,890 --> 00:04:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

49
00:04:55,270 --> 00:04:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I'm to tail one... 
it should be this one.</i></font>

50
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Adventurers tend to stay in the same 
area, so I won't seem unnatural.</i></font>

51
00:05:12,650 --> 00:05:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He turned? I don't think 
there are any inns that way.</i></font>

52
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He could be luring me into a trap.</i></font>

53
00:05:21,350 --> 00:05:23,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How did he know?</i></font>

54
00:05:24,690 --> 00:05:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Perhaps I shouldn't today.</i></font>

55
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I <i>knew</i> it. You're tailing me.</font>

56
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the Blade's...</font>

57
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you were tailing me, 
does that mean you know?</font>

58
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you doing something you 
don't want me to know about?</font>

59
00:05:50,470 --> 00:05:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw you!</font>

60
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just the Blade's toady. 
Don't get fresh with me!</font>

61
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People still think I'm a toady, do they?</font>

62
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't kill him.</font>

63
00:06:02,250 --> 00:06:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how you're begging for your life?</font>

64
00:06:04,820 --> 00:06:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die!</font>

65
00:06:08,470 --> 00:06:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you die.</font>

66
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will he be okay?</font>

67
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be fine.</font>

68
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you. You saved me.</font>

69
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you were tailing some 
weird guy and came running.</font>

70
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, are you still having me watched?</font>

71
00:06:27,650 --> 00:06:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you probably haven't 
noticed this either.</font>

72
00:06:34,810 --> 00:06:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least act a little flustered.</font>

73
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it was you.</font>

74
00:06:39,930 --> 00:06:42,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't notice at first, did you?</font>

75
00:06:42,370 --> 00:06:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never would've noticed if you 
were serious about tailing me.</font>

76
00:06:46,860 --> 00:06:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't trying to avoid detection.</font>

77
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I noticed him.</font>

78
00:06:50,850 --> 00:06:53,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm not like you two.</font>

79
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, who is this guy?</font>

80
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you recall how the 
merchant guild's staff</font>

81
00:07:03,140 --> 00:07:06,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">stole labyrinth goods from Judge's shop?</font>

82
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he's an adventurer.</font>

83
00:07:08,650 --> 00:07:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, an adventurer connected 
to that staff member.</font>

84
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'd get caught if he simply 
sold the stolen goods,</font>

85
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he gave them to an adventurer 
to sell to the guild.</font>

86
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:24,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why nothing turned 
up on the black market.</font>

87
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I had Stud look into it.</font>

88
00:07:29,610 --> 00:07:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found exactly what you described.</font>

89
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Recently, this party has been bringing 
in labyrinth goods above their rank.</font>

90
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He belongs to that party.</font>

91
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have one request.</font>

92
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First thing tomorrow, could you confess 
what you've done to the merchant's guild?</font>

93
00:07:58,690 --> 00:08:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen...</font>

94
00:08:00,370 --> 00:08:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

95
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have to go there themselves.</font>

96
00:08:05,970 --> 00:08:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to rouse 
suspicion by hurting them.</font>

97
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want me to do it, then?</font>

98
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

99
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do that?</font>

100
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want it done tomorrow morning, right?</font>

101
00:08:16,410 --> 00:08:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I won't 
leave any visible marks.</font>

102
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, perhaps 
I'll have you do that.</font>

103
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got this.</font>

104
00:08:24,970 --> 00:08:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your last chance.</font>

105
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you confess your crimes to 
the merchant's guild tomorrow?</font>

106
00:08:36,210 --> 00:08:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will. I will, so please—</font>

107
00:08:41,340 --> 00:08:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a shame.</font>

108
00:08:45,490 --> 00:08:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's really <i>such</i> a shame.</font>

109
00:08:46,950 --> 00:08:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't hurt him too much.</font>

110
00:08:49,610 --> 00:08:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

111
00:08:51,590 --> 00:08:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His party's in on it, too. 
Please get all of their names.</font>

112
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

113
00:08:57,330 --> 00:09:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure he won't say we 
threatened him for information.</font>

114
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And don't give him a 
reason to hold a grudge.</font>

115
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I know.</font>

116
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:12,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move him.</font>

117
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Take him to base number 
two. It's soundproof.</font>

118
00:09:13,690 --> 00:09:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was one of them watching me, too?</i></font>

119
00:09:18,010 --> 00:09:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-Don't!</font>

120
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have this resolved 
by tomorrow morning.</font>

121
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bit late now, but should I 
have asked him to do that for free?</font>

122
00:09:34,980 --> 00:09:40,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not? Think of it as his 
way of making it up to you.</font>

123
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:42,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

124
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And don't go places 
like that by yourself.</font>

125
00:09:44,430 --> 00:09:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, please. I assumed 
you'd be coming with me.</font>

126
00:09:56,610 --> 00:10:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder if they won't 
take me seriously again.</i></font>

127
00:10:00,130 --> 00:10:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But Mr. Lizel might want 
the stolen goods someday.</i></font>

128
00:10:05,070 --> 00:10:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The merchant's guild has 
really gone downhill.</font>

129
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard the damage was pretty severe.</font>

130
00:10:13,230 --> 00:10:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say someone went 
to complain every day.</font>

131
00:10:17,010 --> 00:10:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe it was a 
high-ranking staff member.</font>

132
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be?</font>

133
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What's the meaning of this?</font>

134
00:10:25,610 --> 00:10:28,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you going to take 
responsibility for this?</font>

135
00:10:28,230 --> 00:10:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We demand a guarantee!</font>

136
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An apology won't cut it!</font>

137
00:10:35,050 --> 00:10:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me...</font>

138
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One moment, plea—</font>

139
00:10:39,570 --> 00:10:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're terribly sorry for the 
inconvenience caused by our incompetence!</font>

140
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

141
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the stolen items have been recovered.</font>

142
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way, please.</font>

143
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are those items.</font>

144
00:10:56,600 --> 00:11:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once again, we're terribly 
sorry for what happened.</font>

145
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please raise your head.</font>

146
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for recovering the goods.</font>

147
00:11:09,090 --> 00:11:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again, we're terribly sorry.</font>

148
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, may I ask what happened?</font>

149
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:16,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

150
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This morning, a group of 
adventurers came to the guild.</font>

151
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They confessed to working with 
guild staff to sell stolen goods.</font>

152
00:11:29,970 --> 00:11:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because they named their accomplice, 
rumors spread instantly.</font>

153
00:11:36,460 --> 00:11:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened to the staff member?</font>

154
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He noticed the commotion 
and attempted to flee.</font>

155
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was arrested by some officers 
who found him suspicious.</font>

156
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll work with the police to ensure 
the staff member is justly punished.</font>

157
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll let you know as soon 
as a decision's been made.</font>

158
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's all right. I'm just 
glad I got my goods back.</font>

159
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'll excuse me.</font>

160
00:12:05,310 --> 00:12:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for stopping by.</font>

161
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's what happened.</font>

162
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was worried since you'd 
seemed down recently.</font>

163
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

164
00:12:20,990 --> 00:12:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, um...</font>

165
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, me?</font>

166
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Eleven, and I'm currently convincing 
them to let me join their party.</font>

167
00:12:30,890 --> 00:12:32,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you!</font>

168
00:12:32,340 --> 00:12:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

169
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so surprised?</font>

170
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

171
00:12:44,070 --> 00:12:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Lizel, um...</font>

172
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you really going to 
let him join your party?</font>

173
00:12:52,450 --> 00:12:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't seem like a good idea.</font>

174
00:12:56,010 --> 00:12:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Spoken like a true appraiser.</i></font>

175
00:12:58,470 --> 00:12:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you disapprove?</font>

176
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just think if you're letting</font>

177
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">someone join your party,
they should be more, well...</font>

178
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:11,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. He hasn't joined us yet.</font>

179
00:13:11,410 --> 00:13:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Really? Never mind, then.</font>

180
00:13:16,140 --> 00:13:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you really don't want him 
to join us, I won't let him.</font>

181
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait!</font>

182
00:13:22,010 --> 00:13:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Judge, right?</font>

183
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you really against me 
joining their party? Why?</font>

184
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Mr. Lizel, help—</font>

185
00:13:32,460 --> 00:13:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think about this?</font>

186
00:13:34,620 --> 00:13:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, why?</font>

187
00:13:38,370 --> 00:13:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Ask Stud!</font>

188
00:13:40,730 --> 00:13:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

189
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He actually left.</font>

190
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He must be stupid.</font>

191
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:54,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, there's no merchant's 
guild in Marcade, is there?</font>

192
00:13:54,690 --> 00:13:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

193
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f4f2f1">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

