200
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="22">Inspect &
Provide Services</font></font></font>

201
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#eee9d9">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

202
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="22">Shop</font></font></font>

203
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're basically self-governed.</font>

204
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f4f2f1">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

205
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="28">Marcade</font></font></font>

206
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f2f0e9">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

207
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="24">Local Lord</font></font></font>

208
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#8bd5b2">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

209
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="19">No restrictions
