210
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ede8d8">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

211
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ede8d8">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

212
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="24">Man      age</font></font></font>

213
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#89d5b0">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

214
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="26">May join guild
if desired</font></font></font>

215
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ede8d8">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

216
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="24">Shop</font></font></font>

217
00:13:59,550 --> 00:14:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lord manages everything directly.</font>

218
00:14:03,180 --> 00:14:06,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Mr. Insigh registered with the guild?</font>

219
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

220
00:14:08,190 --> 00:14:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trading merchants frequently deal with 
other nations, so it's necessary.</font>

221
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'm sure he'll hear about this.</font>

222
00:14:18,110 --> 00:14:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I actually sent him a letter 
saying you seemed down recently.</font>

223
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

224
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said I wanted to give
you something to cheer you up</font>

225
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and asked about your preferences.</font>

226
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he'll be able 
to connect the dots.</font>

227
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

228
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He might think I'm a pathetic shopkeeper.</i></font>

229
00:14:42,070 --> 00:14:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I not have done that?</font>

230
00:14:44,970 --> 00:14:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no.</font>

231
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:49,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your concern for me is, um...</font>

232
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">very much appreciated.</font>

233
00:14:54,820 --> 00:15:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If that doting grandfather hears about 
this, worst case, he could quit the guild.</i></font>

234
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The guild is screwed if they 
lose someone that big.</i></font>

235
00:15:06,140 --> 00:15:08,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Does this guy know that?</i></font>

236
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we get something to eat to 
celebrate the situation being resolved?</font>

237
00:15:12,490 --> 00:15:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be my treat.</font>

238
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'd love to go.</font>

239
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but let me pay for it.</font>

240
00:15:19,710 --> 00:15:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if he does, he 
probably doesn't care.</i></font>

241
00:15:40,470 --> 00:15:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sit with me.</font>

242
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. The boss would kill me.</font>

243
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you my shadow today?</font>

244
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:53,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something like that.</font>

245
00:15:53,540 --> 00:15:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for last night.</font>

246
00:15:56,490 --> 00:15:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get enough sleep?</font>

247
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what you're worried 
about? I'm fine.</font>

248
00:16:03,890 --> 00:16:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, did you need something from me?</font>

249
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was pleased to have spotted my shadow 
for the first time and called you over.</font>

250
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you serious?</font>

251
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:21,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, since you're here, maybe you 
could tell me about your boss.</font>

252
00:16:21,730 --> 00:16:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what?</font>

253
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything. Perhaps his behavior 
has improved recently.</font>

254
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It hasn't.</i></font>

255
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If my answers determine whether he joins 
their party or not, I could lose my head.</i></font>

256
00:16:36,590 --> 00:16:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. You can tell me 
exactly what he's like.</font>

257
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, his attitude towards you 
guys changed a few days ago.</font>

258
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:50,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not so much watching 
you as guarding you.</font>

259
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guarding me?</font>

260
00:16:51,590 --> 00:16:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He doesn't want you to have any problems.</font>

261
00:16:54,990 --> 00:16:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did yesterday go?</font>

262
00:16:57,330 --> 00:17:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may have been too casual 
about asking him to do that.</font>

263
00:17:01,170 --> 00:17:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anything, he seemed happy about it.</font>

264
00:17:04,140 --> 00:17:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He felt like you were counting on him.</font>

265
00:17:06,930 --> 00:17:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to have known 
him for a long time.</font>

266
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've known him since he joined the gang.</font>

267
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:19,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So are some subordinates just 
fodder, while others aren't?</i></font>

268
00:17:22,290 --> 00:17:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have another question.</font>

269
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How would you feel if I killed 
many of the gang's underlings</font>

270
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:31,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">aside from elite members like you?</font>

271
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:34,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're all disposable.</font>

272
00:17:34,050 --> 00:17:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anything, us underlings should 
be honored to be killed by you.</font>

273
00:17:40,690 --> 00:17:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then... tell him</font>

274
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to come see me tomorrow morning.</font>

275
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:52,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You probably meant what you said.</font>

276
00:17:57,500 --> 00:18:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I would never kill you.</font>

277
00:18:12,730 --> 00:18:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two have gotten really friendly.</font>

278
00:18:15,870 --> 00:18:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I say you could talk to him?</font>

279
00:18:18,530 --> 00:18:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He called me over.</font>

280
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did? Really? And you 
let him see your face?</font>

281
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:32,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got to meet him last night, but 
don't let that get to your head.</font>

282
00:18:32,560 --> 00:18:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This guy's about to kill me.</i></font>

283
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you return, if you don't report 
every word that was said, I'll kill you.</font>

284
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning!</font>

285
00:18:48,150 --> 00:18:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're back?</font>

286
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He invited me today.</font>

287
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:55,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he still asleep?</font>

288
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He usually is at this hour unless 
he's got something to do.</font>

289
00:19:00,150 --> 00:19:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

290
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's you. Did you come to 
complain to Mr. Lizel again?</font>

291
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm here on an errand today.</font>

292
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:11,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, he's still asleep.</font>

293
00:19:11,620 --> 00:19:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's no good.</font>

294
00:19:14,800 --> 00:19:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's someone who'd 
like to see him today.</font>

295
00:19:18,020 --> 00:19:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I wake him?</font>

296
00:19:20,730 --> 00:19:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, plea—</font>

297
00:19:23,140 --> 00:19:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What if you broke it?!</font>

298
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:29,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

299
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you heard, but 
he's still asleep.</font>

300
00:19:35,800 --> 00:19:37,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So?</font>

301
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait until he wakes up.</font>

302
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:42,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here on behalf of a busy man.</font>

303
00:19:42,570 --> 00:19:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, so wait until he wakes up so you 
can take him with you right away.</font>

304
00:19:48,320 --> 00:19:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get that through your stupid head, loser.</font>

305
00:19:53,990 --> 00:19:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you realize I'm a police officer, 
and you're obstructing my duties?</font>

306
00:19:59,300 --> 00:20:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I do. I hate the police.</font>

307
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop right there!</font>

308
00:20:12,140 --> 00:20:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting you kill 
each other on my doorstep!</font>

309
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me.</font>

310
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, Captain. You're here as well.</font>

311
00:20:27,910 --> 00:20:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning.</font>

312
00:20:29,730 --> 00:20:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies for keeping you waiting.</font>

313
00:20:31,620 --> 00:20:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

314
00:20:33,350 --> 00:20:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, you've got something to do, right?</font>

315
00:20:35,860 --> 00:20:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

316
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has time for me today, does he?</font>

317
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we go?</font>

318
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no time. Let's hurry.</font>

319
00:20:53,930 --> 00:20:55,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While I still have the 
chance, let me ask you.</font>

320
00:20:56,500 --> 00:21:00,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you still want to join my party?</font>

321
00:21:00,770 --> 00:21:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, obviously.</font>

322
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

323
00:21:04,570 --> 00:21:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Because...</font>

324
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:15,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At first I was just curious, 
but since then...</i></font>

325
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

326
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some huge shopkeeper hates my guts.</font>

327
00:21:24,870 --> 00:21:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he does.</font>

328
00:21:26,130 --> 00:21:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

329
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you serve that guy, anyway?</font>

330
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:35,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want nothing from him.</font>

331
00:21:35,370 --> 00:21:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My only and greatest joy is 
to grant him his desires.</font>

332
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sound like a fanatic.</font>

333
00:21:44,230 --> 00:21:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't compare me to those who 
seek something in return.</font>

334
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh...</i></font>

335
00:21:57,050 --> 00:21:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's how it is.</i></font>

336
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be with you. 
Let me be with you.</font>

337
00:22:05,610 --> 00:22:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's do what has to be done.</font>

338
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#413d37">Next Time</font></font></font>

339
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#24262a">"Welcome to the Party"</font></font></font>

340
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: "Welcome to the Party."</font>

341
00:23:45,020 --> 00:23:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#eaf2fc"><font size="20">Illustration by: <font size="24">Ugonba</font></font></font></font></font>

